  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO ALLOW AN HONORABLY DISCHARGED MEMBER OF THE UNITED STATES ARMED FORCES, UPON PRESENTATION TO THE ISSUING OFFICIAL OF A VALID DD FORM 214, TO RECEIVE AT NO COST ONE REGULAR OR MILITARY LICENSE TAG, OR A SPECIAL OR PERSONALIZED TAG AT ONLY THE COST OF THE ADDITIONAL FEE; TO AMEND SECTIONS 27-19-5, 27-19-11 AND 27-19-43, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM; TO BRING FORWARD SECTIONS 27-19-35 AND 27-19-51, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, FOR THE PURPOSE OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
